#program name- Program to find the area and circumference of a circle, when the radius is entered by the user. 
#               However, the user can input radius in integer or float.



r=eval(input("enter the radius"))
c=2*3.141*r
a=3.141*r*r
print("circumference",c)
print("area=",a)
